This custom stylesheet aims to relax the default Firefox large-floating-boxes UI design.

Changes:
1. Minimized rounding
2. Reduced tab and navbar height
3. Toggled dynamically sized tabs
4. Reduced menu and icon spacing
5. Concealed sidebar title
6. Concealed tabs toolbar icons

Tested resolutions:
* 1920x1200
* 1920x1080

To report broken layout, please open an issue in this repository and mention your browser window resolution.
